54
00:10:05,950 --> 00:10:08,830
Fine, just to celebrate getting out of there.

55
00:10:08,830 --> 00:10:10,540
Alright, food!

56
00:10:18,410 --> 00:10:19,750
Gotta be good now, right?

57
00:10:20,410 --> 00:10:21,580
Yeah.

58
00:10:31,370 --> 00:10:32,370
Here.

59
00:10:32,370 --> 00:10:34,370
It's our last can.

60
00:10:34,830 --> 00:10:35,830
Right!

61
00:10:35,830 --> 00:10:36,830
Hot!

62
00:10:44,330 --> 00:10:46,290
So good!

63
