79
00:13:01,950 --> 00:13:04,000
No, I'm good.

80
00:13:04,660 --> 00:13:06,370
You're a terrible shot, anyway.

81
00:13:06,950 --> 00:13:08,330
Oh, shut up.

82
00:13:08,580 --> 00:13:10,870
You don't carry a weapon?

83
00:13:10,870 --> 00:13:12,750
I don't need one.

84
00:13:17,950 --> 00:13:20,040
But there are so many.

85
00:13:20,040 --> 00:13:22,040
