86
00:13:22,250 --> 00:13:26,000
But I guess I could go look for one.

87
00:13:27,370 --> 00:13:31,790
It doesn't have to be a weapon.
We might find something we could use.

88
00:13:32,450 --> 00:13:34,750
Maybe we'll find food.

89
00:13:34,750 --> 00:13:37,450
No, if we're looking for food here,

90
00:13:37,450 --> 00:13:40,870
we'll either find something like rations, or find...

91
00:13:42,830 --> 00:13:44,080
Machine gun.

92
00:13:45,950 --> 00:13:47,250
Shells.

93
00:13:48,120 --> 00:13:49,500
Tank.

94
00:14:00,500 --> 00:14:03,700
