108
00:14:57,950 --> 00:14:59,660
You wanna fly too, right, Chi?

109
00:14:59,660 --> 00:15:01,500
Nope, not at all.

110
00:15:12,290 --> 00:15:14,290
Is this a weapon, too?

111
00:15:15,540 --> 00:15:17,290
I dunno.

112
00:15:17,750 --> 00:15:22,950
But it was probably a bomber or something...

113
00:15:28,370 --> 00:15:31,000
War means killing one another, right?

114
00:15:31,000 --> 00:15:33,290
Why'd they do that?

115
00:15:34,700 --> 00:15:43,660
Dunno. Their interests probably didn't
coincide with... the other side's!

116
00:15:54,580 --> 00:15:59,750
So like, if there are three people,
but only enough food for two...

117
00:15:59,750 --> 00:16:03,250
I bet that's when you've gotta
get your weapon and fight.

118
00:16:03,620 --> 00:16:05,660
Same now, same then...

119
00:16:07,330 --> 00:16:08,540
Huh?

120
00:16:18,450 --> 00:16:20,290
There's a lotta different kinds.

121
