Hey!

154
00:19:32,160 --> 00:19:33,370
Don't move.

155
00:19:35,450 --> 00:19:36,950
What are you doing?

156
00:19:37,160 --> 00:19:39,250
I'm taking it.

157
00:19:59,910 --> 00:20:04,120
I see. I should've carried a weapon too, huh...

158
00:20:04,830 --> 00:20:05,910
Yep.

159
00:20:06,370 --> 00:20:08,700
